Mia Marvin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mia_Marvin 0 Mia Marvin (November 1, 1904 – September 27, 1992) was an American actress best known for her role in The Public Enemy as the woman who houses and seduces James Cagney. In her entire film career spanning five years she appeared in only three movies in her career but never in a credited role.
